       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       PGM-SORTIO.
           SORT TRAB ASCENDING KEY COD-TRAB
               INPUT PROCEDURE ROT-ENT 
               OUTPUT PROCEDURE ROT-SAI.
           STOP RUN.

       ROT-ENT SECTION.
           PERFORM INICIO-ENT.
           PERFORM PRINCIPAL-ENT UNTIL FIM-ARQ EQUAL "SIM".
           PERFORM FIM-ENT.
       INICIO-ENT SECTION.
           OPEN INPUT ENTRADA.
           PERFORM LEITURA-ENT.

       LEITURA-ENT SECTION.
           READ ENTRADA AT END MOVE "SIM" TO FIM-ARQ.

       PRINCIPAL-ENT SECTION.
           PERFORM SELECAO-ENT.
           PERFORM LEITURA-ENT.

       SELECAO-ENT SECTION.
           IF SEXO-ENT EQUAL "M"
           PERFORM GRAVACAO-ENT.

       GRAVACAO-ENT SECTION.
           MOVE COD-ENT TO COD-TRAB.
           MOVE SEXO-ENT TO SEXO-TRAB.
           MOVE NOME-ENT TO NOME-TRAB.
           RELEASE REG-TRAB.

       FIM-ENT SECTION.
           CLOSE ENTRADA.

       ROT-SAI SECTION.
           PERFORM INICIO-SAI.
           PERFORM PRINCIPAL-SAI UNTIL FIM-ARQ EQUAL "SIM".
           PERFORM FIM-SAI.

       INICIO-SAI SECTION.
           MOVE "NAO" TO FIM-ARQ.
           OPEN OUTPUT RELAT.
           PERFORM LEITURA-SAI.

       LEITURA-SAI SECTION.
           RETURN TRAB AT END MOVE "SIM" TO FIM-ARQ.

       PRINCIPAL-SAI SECTION.
           PERFORM IMPRESSAO-SAI.
           PERFORM LEITURA-SAI.

       IMPRESSAO-SAI SECTION.
           IF CT-LIN GREATER THAN 24
               PERFORM CABECALHO-SAI.
           PERFORM DETALHE-SAI.

       CABECALHO-SAI SECTION.
           ADD 1 TO CT-PAG.
           MOVE CT-PAG TO VAR-PAG.
           MOVE SPACES TO REG-REL.
           WRITE REG-REL AFTER ADVANCING PAGE.
           WRITE REG-REL FROM CAB-01 AFTER ADVANCING 1 LINE.
           WRITE REG-REL FROM CAB-02 AFTER ADVANCING 2 LINES.
           WRITE REG-REL FROM CAB-03 AFTER ADVANCING 2 LINES.
           MOVE ZEROES TO CT-LIN.

        DETALHE-SAI SECTION.
           MOVE COD-TRAB TO COD-DET.
           MOVE SEXO-TRAB TO SEXO-DET.
           MOVE NOME-TRAB TO NOME-DET.
           WRITE REG-REL FROM DETALHE AFTER ADVANCING 1 LINE.
           ADD 1 TO CT-LIN.

       FIM-SAI SECTION.
           CLOSE RELAT.